## Accessibility & UX Issues Summary

### CRITICAL (Must Fix Immediately) ðŸ”´

1. **Dark Theme Contrast Failure**
   - **Impact:** HIGH - Makes primary content unreadable
   - **Affected Elements:** 
     - All page titles (H1 headings)
     - Section headings (H2, H3)
     - Some button text in hero sections
   - **Root Cause:** CSS not properly applying light colors to text in dark theme
   - **Fix Required:** Update theme CSS to use appropriate text colors for dark backgrounds

### MEDIUM (Should Fix) ðŸŸ¡

2. **URL Structure Issues**
   - **Impact:** MEDIUM - Poor SEO and user experience
   - **Issue:** URLs contain unencoded spaces
   - **Example:** `/services / it-support-services /help desk support`
   - **Fix Required:** Implement proper URL slugs (kebab-case)

### MINOR (Nice to Have) ðŸŸ¢

